messages.content: describe the contents of this image.

The image contains an email exchange between Andrew Sung and Jazib Haider regarding a project. Andrew, who works at AMC Engineering, is asking Jazib for paperwork related to fill/backfill material for a playground upgrade. Jazib, the founder of Serene Project Controls, responds that he has left a voicemail and will provide the paperwork soon. This is from "mxroute issue.png," Section 0.
